parameters:
\n<Rui>Is this hole... a garbage chute? And there's a
large fan above it.

\n<Rui>To stop the power and go through the fan...? But
there's no switch, and it's too high up.

\n<Rui>...Damn it! If I die here, I'll curse that eyeball
demon for the rest of my life!!!
\n<Rui>This time, I'll make sure to escape!
